---
title: Cheddar, Courgette & Carrot Fritters with Roasted Kumara Salad & Herby Mayo
description: There's no better way to get your veggies than by adding them to cheesy golden fritters, gently pan-fried for a gorgeous finish. With an extra dose of goodness from the robust side salad and a drizzle of delicious herby mayo, this is a colourful garden medley that you'll love!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/courgette-fritters-cheese-0dc3e7e4.jpg
